Program: Outlook
Title: 11/02/2010
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0063g3n
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 12 Feb 2010
Personal stories behind the news from all over the world. With Lucy Ash. Kenyan riot witness; former dot.com millionaire. Kenyan ICC We hear from the Kenyan man who is risking his life to tell international prosecutors what he saw in the run up to his country's deadly post election riots. As a result of taking a stand, he has had to flee his home and lose his business. Benjamin Cohen A former teenage dot.com millionaire tells us about the boom and bust of his internet empire, and how he was once called out of school for a business meeting with Benjamin Netanyahu. Show less